"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:5.18.1.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">5.18.1.2</span> 标题：陶罐（clay jar）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：כַּד</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kad)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:14\">GEN 24:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:15\">GEN 24:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:16\">GEN 24:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:17\">GEN 24:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:18\">GEN 24:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:20\">GEN 24:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:43\">GEN 24:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:45\">GEN 24:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:46\">GEN 24:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:16\">JDG 7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:16\">JDG 7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:19\">JDG 7:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:20\">JDG 7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:12\">1KI 17:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:14\">1KI 17:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:16\">1KI 17:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:34\">1KI 18:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:6\">ECC 12:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：נֵבֶל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：nevel)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:14\">ISA 30:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:2\">LAM 4:2</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：צַפַּחַת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tsapachath)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:12\">1SA 26:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:16\">1SA 26:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:12\">1KI 17:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:14\">1KI 17:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:16\">1KI 17:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:6\">1KI 19:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κεράμιον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：keramion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:13\">MRK 14:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:10\">LUK 22:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ὑδρία</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：hudria)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:28\">JHN 4:28</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0059_women_drawing_water_into_jars.png\" alt=\"OAI-0059_women_drawing_water_into_jars\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\"> (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>陶罐是一种陶制器皿，用来储存葡萄酒和橄榄油等液体（另参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">5.18.1 储存容器 (containers for storage)&lt;REALIA:5.18.1&gt;</a> ）。陶罐也可以用来装水或其他液体。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>石缸（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">5.18.1.1 石缸 (stone jar)&lt;REALIA:5.18.1.1&gt;</a> ）只是用来储水。陶罐与石缸不同，装满水后必须要足够轻，以便妇女能够拿着走路；在当时的社会，打水工作通常由妇女来做。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:6\">JHN 2:6</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:28\">JHN 4:28</a> 中，约翰使用了同一个意为“罐”的希腊文词语（《和修》2:6译作“缸”，4:28“水罐”），但从上下文可以清楚地看出，这个词指的是两种不同的容器。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:28\">JHN 4:28</a> 提到的妇女不可能提着一口沉重的石缸。大多数译本都译为“水罐”（“water jar”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）。目标语言如果使用不同的词语来分别表示打水或提水的器皿与喝水的器皿，就应使用表示前者的词语。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
